Celebrate Magical Events at Disney Store













Events take place every day at 3pm all summer long! Participate in an event each week and receive a FREE embroidered patch.*Select stores only. Call your local store for details.
LEARN MORE & SEE AVAILABLE GIVEAWAYS


Disney Store Opening Ceremony
Join us for a magical opening ceremony every day! One Guest is selected daily to help open the Disney Store.
SEE AVAILABLE GIVEAWAY


Move along, dance, sing and become immersed in exciting worlds from Disney films and TV shows.
SEE AVAILABLE SHOWTIME EVENTS


Enjoy hearing your favorite Disney, Pixar, Marvel and Star Wars stories come to life during interactive Story Time events. 
SEE AVAILABLE GIVEAWAY


Walt Disney was an innovator who continuously made advances in animation which continues today at The Walt Disney Company.
Want to get started now? Learn how to draw Tinker Bell using this video.
DRAW TINKER BELL


Test your knowledge of all things Disney, Pixar, Marvel and Star Wars.
LEARN MORE




Call your local store and speak with a Cast Member for event details and times.
*While supplies last. Guest must participate in the event to receive a giveaway. Minimum age for participation is 3 years. Event is limited based on store capacity.
	No lineups prior to 30 minutes before event begins. Events are subject to change or cancellation without notice. In-store events are limited at Disney Store Outlets.



Make Your Day Special at Disney Store


BIRTHDAYS
If it's your special occasion, let a Cast Member know so they can sprinkle some pixie dust and bring a smile to your face.



CONGRATULATIONS
If you are celebrating something special, let a Cast Member know so they can make some Disney magic for you.



PARKS VACATION
We love making your day extra magical! If you have booked a vacation to Disneyland Resort in California or Walt Disney World in Florida, tell a Cast Member and we'll celebrate your trip with you! If you would like to surprise your family, phone your local store ahead of your visit.




