Charitable Giving 



Through contributions, collaborating with nonprofit organizations, in-kind gifts and employee volunteerism, Disney brings positive, lasting change to communities around the world.














$400M Philanthropic Giving 


Our Giving In 2016, Disney gave more than 400 million to nonprofit organizations helping kids, families, and communities in need through charitable cash giving, in-kind and product contributions, and public service announcements.











23.1M Books Donated 


Book Donations Since 2012, Disney has donated 23.1 million books to schools and children.







