Be Inspired 



At Disney, we believe that our concern for kids and families must extend beyond their entertainment to the world in which they live. We aim to inspire people to think creatively, live healthier, conserve nature and strengthen our communities.
View the Official Be Inspired Website

















Strengthen Communities Disney is committed to strengthening communities by providing hope, happiness, and comfort to kids and families who need it most.
View More














Healthy Living We seek to engage kids and families in living healthier lifestyles through The Walt Disney Company Healthy Living commitment. This includes The Mickey Check, a quick and easy way for families to identify healthier food options in stores, on-line, on-air, at Disney theme parks and other places where licensed Disney products are sold.
