Magic Your Way Vacation Packages




Create a magical family vacation when you stay and play in a never-ending world of enchantment!



Book Your Vacation Package






Sample Vacation Packages



Begin building your dream vacation by choosing from over 25 Disney Resort hotels and then customize a package that lets you take advantage of all 4 theme parks, our 2 water parks and over 150 Walt Disney World restaurant and dining locations!    Not sure which to pick? Before getting started, take a look at these sample vacation packages currently being offered:  Room & Ticket Package 6-night, 7-day vacation packages with tickets valid at all 4 theme parks, for as little as $93 per person, per day for a family of 4 staying at select Disney’s All-Star Resorts. Total package price: $2,587*  Room, Ticket & Dine Package 6-night, 7-day vacation packages with the Disney Quick-Service Dining Plan and tickets valid at all 4 theme parks, for as little as $128 per person, per day for a family of 4 staying at select Disney’s All-Star Resorts. Total package price: $3,581*    Want even more magic? Your Magic Your Way package also comes with Magical Extras like dining and entertainment discounts—and complimentary mini-golf vouchers!  Start Planning Your Vacation Package   *Sample Package Details Sample prices are based on 2 adults, one junior and one child in a standard room at select Disney All-Star Resorts for select 2017 dates: February 26 through March 9; April 23 through May 25; August 13 through October 5; October 9 through November 17; November 25 through December 14. The number of rooms allocated for these packages may be limited. Magic Your Way® Tickets valid for one theme park per day and must be used within 14 days of first use.






Explore the Benefits of Staying at a Disney Resort Hotel



As a Disney Resort hotel Guest, you can enjoy an array of special benefits designed to make your vacation as convenient as it is magical:








Early Access to FastPass+ Planning – Enjoy first access to Disney FastPass+ experiences—up to 60 days before check-in!








Extra Magic Hours – Make the most of your vacation by spending additional time at a different theme park each day—valid theme park ticket and Resort ID required. Plus, you’ll also have the chance to enjoy “Extra” Extra Magic Hours only at Pandora – The World of Avatar—available May 27 through July 4, 2017 from 11:00 PM to 1:00 AM, and available July 5 through August 19, 2017 from 10:00 PM to midnight.








Complimentary Resort Transportation and Parking – Motor coaches, ferryboats and our world-famous monorail provide convenient ways to explore all the parks at Walt Disney World Resort. Plus, enjoy complimentary standard parking at all theme parks and Resort hotels!








Complimentary Airport Transportation – Skip baggage claim with Disney’s Magical Express service, convenient motorcoach transportation and luggage delivery for you and your party between Orlando International Airport and your Disney Resort hotel.








Complimentary MagicBands  – Each Resort hotel Guest will receive a personalized MagicBand—available in a rainbow of colors!








Disney Dining Plan Access – Adding one of our unique dining plans to a Magic Your Way Vacation Package gives you the flexibility and convenience to enjoy prepaid meals and snacks throughout Walt Disney World Resort. With several options to choose from, it’s easy to find the dining plan that best fits your family’s needs.






The Magic is Endless



Imagine a place like nowhere else on Earth, where moments and memories have no limit.   Disney's Hollywood Studios  Make your way to a galaxy far, far away with attractions and entertainment that celebrate the Star Wars universe.  Epcot  Set sail through Arendelle, meet Anna and Elsa inside their Royal Sommerhus and enjoy the Frozen fun happening at Norway Pavilion.   Disney's Animal Kingdom Theme Park  Experience dazzling day and nighttime attractions, wild animal encounters and entertainment for all ages.     Magic Kingdom Park Frolic to enchanted lands where jubilant parades, magical makeovers and fairytale adventures come true. 



  


For assistance with your Walt Disney World visit, please call (407) 939-5277.7:00 AM to 11:00 PM Eastern Time. Guests under 18 years of age must have parent or guardian permission to call.
